A workflow representation should satisfy the Galaxy requirements

[%hardbreaks]
[small]#*_Concreteness:_* __abstract|concrete__#
[small]#*_Strength:_*     __mandatory|recommended|optional__#
[small]#*_Category:_*     __WG1__,__WG2__,__WG3__,__WG4__#
[small]#*_Status:_*       __draft|final|deprecated__#

A workflow representation contains at least the following specification elements:

|===
| Annotation element |Â Description

| `@main_Desc`
| To specify information about the workflow.

| `@main_inputs`
| To specify the inputs parameters of the workflow.

| `@main_outputs`
| To specify the output parameters of the workflow.

| `@steps`
| To specify the steps of the workflows.
|===


